         <ab/>
         <div type="edition">
            <note>Whenever possible, the incipits have been taken from <bibl><ptr target="bm:Rome1952Saatat"/></bibl>.</note>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Basalam">
               <label>Introductory prayers (Ba-salām ʾǝmḫāba ʾǝgziʾābǝḥer ʾab…) </label>
               <ab>
                  
               </ab>
               <note>see <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:SalotaEtan1951"/>, <citedRange unit="page">20-22</citedRange>
                  </bibl>.
               </note>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Tawakkafetan">
               <label>Prayer of offering incense (Tawakkaf ʾǝgziʾo ʾǝṭānana…)</label>
               <note>See <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:SalotaEtan1951"/>, <citedRange unit="page">123</citedRange>
                  </bibl>.
               </note>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Nesel">
               <label> Supplication for offering the incense (Nǝsǝʾǝl wa-nāstabaqqʷǝʾ ḫiruta śannāyātika ʾǝgziʾo…) </label>
               <note>See <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:SalotaEtan1951"/>, <citedRange unit="page">147</citedRange>
                  </bibl>.
               </note>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Egziabherabiy">
               <label> ʾƎgziʾābǝḥer ʿabiy wǝʾǝtu la-ʿālam ba-qadāmi za-ʾi-yaḫallǝq…</label>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Tawakkafemneya">
               <label>Prayer of offering incense (Tawakkaf ʾǝmǝnneya ʾəgziʾo, ʾana ḫāṭǝʾ wa-ʾabāsi, zanta ʿǝṭāna nəṣuḥa…) </label>
               <ab>
                  ተወከፍ፡ እምኔየ፡ እግዚኦ፤ አነ፡ ኃጥእ፡ ወአባሲ፤ ዘንተ፡ ዕጣነ፡ ንጹሐ፡ ለስርየተ፡ ኀጢአትየ፡ ወለኵሉ፡ ሕዝብከ። 
                  ተወከፈኒ፡ ጸሎትየ፡ ከመ፡ ዕጣን፡ በቅድሜከ። ስምዐኒ፡ አምላኪየ፡ ስእለትየ፤ እማዕምቅ፡ ጸዋዕኩ፡ እግዚኦ።
               </ab>
               <note>See <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:Rome1952Saatat"/>, <citedRange unit="page">383</citedRange>
                  </bibl>.
               </note>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Neselakka">
               <label>Supplication for offering the incense (ʾƎsǝʾǝlakka ʾəgziʾo wa-ʾāstabaqqʷǝʿakka bakama 
                  śamarka qʷǝrbāna ʾAbel fəqurəka wa-maśwāʿta Henok wa-Noḫ wa-ʾAbrəhām…) </label>
               <ab>
                  እስእለከ፡ እግዚኦ፡ ወኣስተበቍዐከ፡ በከመ፡ ሠመርከ፡ ቍርባነ፡ አቤል፡ ፍቁርከ፡ ወመሥዋዕተ፡ ሄኖክ፡ ወኖኅ፡ ወአብርሃም።
               </ab>
               <note>See <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:Rome1952Saatat"/>, <citedRange unit="page"> 383-384</citedRange>
                  </bibl>, and <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:SalotaEtan1951"/>, <citedRange unit="page">131</citedRange>
                  </bibl>.
               </note>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Monitions">
               <label>Monitions</label>
               <note>See <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:Rome1952Saatat"/>, <citedRange unit="page">384</citedRange>
                  </bibl>, and <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:SalotaEtan1951"/>, <citedRange unit="page">131-132</citedRange>
                  </bibl>.
               </note>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Sagga">
               <label>Benediction (Ṣaggā za-ʾab wa-ḫirut za-wald sutāfe za-manfas qəddus tafāqǝro za-ʾəgzəʾtəna Māryām…) </label>
               <ab>
                  ጸጋ፡ ዘአብ፡ ወኂሩት፡ ዘወልድ፡ ሱታፌ፡ ዘመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ተፋቅሮ፡ ዘእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘነቢያት፡
                  ወሐዋርያት፡ ዘጻድቃን፡ ወሰማዕት፡ ዘደናግል፡ ወመነኮሳት፡ ዘትጉሃን፡ መላእክት፡ ዘአበው፡ ቀደምት፡ 
                  የሀሉ፡ ምስሌየ፡ ወምስለ፡ ኵልክሙ። አሜን።
               </ab>
               <note>See <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:Rome1952Saatat"/>, <citedRange unit="page">394</citedRange>
                  </bibl>, and <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:SalotaEtan1951"/>, <citedRange unit="page">132</citedRange>
                  </bibl>.
               </note>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Egzyahabo">
               <label>Prayer for the hierarchy (ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer yahabbo la-bǝḍuʿ wa-la-qǝddus liqa ṗāṗāsāt…) </label>
               <ab>
                  እግዚአብሔር፡ የሀቦ፡ ለብፁዕ፡ ወለቅዱስ፡ ሊቀ፡ ጳጳሳት፡ አባ፡ <hi rend="rubric">እገሌ፡</hi>
                  ወብፁዕ፡ ወቅዱስ፡ ጳጳስነ፡ አባ፡ <hi rend="rubric">እገሌ፡</hi>
               </ab>
               <note>See <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:Rome1952Saatat"/>, <citedRange unit="page">394-395</citedRange>
                  </bibl>, and <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:SalotaEtan1951"/>, <citedRange unit="page">132-134</citedRange>
                  </bibl>.
               </note>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Abawe">
               <label>Prayer of offering incense (ʾĀbawwǝʿ laka ʿǝṭāna mǝsla ḥarāgit karbe…) </label>
               <ab>
                  ኣበውእ፡ ለከ፡ ዕጣነ፡ ምስለ፡ ሐራጊት፡ ከርቤ፡ ወቀንአት፡ ወሰሊኆት፡ እምነ፡ አልባሲከ።
                  ተወከፈኒ፡ ጸሎትየ፡ ከመ፡ ዕጣን፡ በቅድሜከ። ኣቄርብ፡ ለከ፡ ዘንተ፡ ዕጣነ፡ ቅድሜከ፡ 
                  በእንተ፡ ኀጢአትየ፡ ወበእንተ፡ ኀጢአቶሙ፡ ለሕዝብከ፡ ከመ፡ ትኅድግ፡ አበሳሆሙ፡ 
                  ወትሣሀሎሙ፡ እስመ፡ መሓሪ፡ አንተ፡ ወለከ፡ ስብሐት፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም። አሜን።
               </ab>
               <note>See <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:Rome1952Saatat"/>, <citedRange unit="page">395-396</citedRange>
                  </bibl>, and <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:SalotaEtan1951"/>, <citedRange unit="page">131</citedRange>
                  </bibl>.
               </note>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Nesebhaka">
               <label>Intercessory prayer (Nǝsebbǝḥākka ʾəgziʾo la-ʾaḫāze kʷǝllu ʿālam…) </label>
               <ab>
                  ንሴብሐከ፡ እግዚኦ፡ ለአኃዜ፡ ኵሉ፡ ዓለም፡ አቡሁ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ወመድኀኒነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ 
                  ወንብለከ፤ ሕገ፡ ሰብእ፡ ዘሥጋ፡ እኩይ፡ አናሕሲ፡ ለነ፡ ወለዓለምሰ፡ ኢትትመዐዐነ፤ ወአብዝኅ፡ ምሕረተከ፡ 
                  ላዕሌነ፤ ወፍጡነ፡ ፈኑ፡ ሣህለከ፡ ዲቤነ። 
               </ab>
               <note>See <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:Rome1952Saatat"/>, <citedRange unit="page">396-402</citedRange>
                  </bibl>, and <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:SalotaEtan1951"/>, <citedRange unit="page">137-142</citedRange>
                  </bibl>. This section includes a series of phrases beginning 
                  <foreign xml:lang="gez">Nəsəʾəlakka wa-nāstabaqqʷəʿakka…</foreign>
               </note>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Jeremy">
               <label> Prayer of Jeremy (Wa-ṣallaya ʾErməyās ba-beta maqdas ʾənza yəbl: Qǝddus, qǝddus, qǝddus, ʾanta maʿazā ṭǝʿum…) </label>
               <ab>
                  ወጸለየ፡ ኤርምያስ፡ በቤተ፡ መቅደስ፡ እንዘ፡ ይብል፤ ቅዱስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ቅዱስ፤ አንተ፡ መዐዛ፡ ጥዑም፡ 
                  ለሰብእ፡ ወብርሃን፡ ዘበአማን፡ ዘያበርህ፡ ሊተ፡ እስከ፡ አነ፡ እበጽሕ፡ ቅድሜከ።
               </ab>
               <note>See <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:Rome1952Saatat"/>, <citedRange unit="page">402-403</citedRange>
                  </bibl>, and <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:SalotaEtan1951"/>, <citedRange unit="page">142-143</citedRange>
                  </bibl>.
               </note>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Chrism">
               <label>Prayer for chrism and incense (Nāʾakkʷǝtakka ʾabuhu la-ʾəgziʾǝna wa-madḫanina ʾIyasus Krəstos…)</label>
               <ab>
                  ናአኵተከ፡ አቡሁ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ወመድኀኒነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ወበእንተ፡ ቅድስት፡ ጼና፡ 
                  እስመ፡ አኮ፡ ባሕቲታ፡ እለ፡ ዘፍጥረት፡ አላ፡ ዘመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ለነ፡ ጼና፡ ወሀብከነ።
                  ናአኵተከ፡ በእንተ፡ መንክራተ፡ ምግባር፡ ወኵሎ፡ ጸጋቲከ፡ ዘጸጎከነ፤ በአሐዱ፡ ወልድከ፡ 
                  ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ እግዚእነ፡ ወመድኀኒነ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም። አሜን።
               </ab>
               <note>See <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:Rome1952Saatat"/>, <citedRange unit="page">403</citedRange>
                  </bibl>, and <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:SalotaEtan1951"/>, <citedRange unit="page">152</citedRange>
                  </bibl>.
               </note>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Request">
               <label>Prayer for request (ʾƎgziʾābǝḥer ʾǝgziʾǝya ʾIyasus Krǝstos wa-manfas qǝddus sǝmāʿ ʾəgziʾo zanta sǝʾlata…) </label>
               <ab>
                  እግዚአብሔር፡ እግዚእየ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ስማዕ፡ እግዚኦ፡ ዘንተ፡ ስእለትየ፡ ወፈጽም፡ ሊተ፡ ኵሎ፡ 
                  ፈቃድየ፡ ለገብርከ፡ <hi rend="rubric">እገሌ፡</hi> በብዕለ፡ ስብሐቲከ፡ ወበብዝኀ፡ ምሕረትከ፤
                  ወዘኒ፡ ዘወሀብከኒ፡ ኢትሂደኒ፡ እግዚኦ፤ ሀበኒ፡ ሞገሰ፡ ወሕይወተ፡ ወኀይለ፡ ወጽንዐ፤ አግርር፡ ፀርየ፡ 
                  ወጸላእትየ፤ ወስረይ፡ ሊተ፡ ለገብርከ፡ ኵሎ፡ ኀጢአትየ፡ ወጸሐፍ፡ ስምየ፡ ውስተ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ሕይወት፤
                  ተዘከረኒ፡ በመንግሥትከ፡ ምስለ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ ጻድቃኒከ፡ እለ፡ አሥመሩከ፡ በሕይወቶሙ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም።
                  አሜን።
               </ab>
               <note>See <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:Rome1952Saatat"/>, <citedRange unit="page">403-404</citedRange>
                  </bibl>, and <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:SalotaEtan1951"/>, <citedRange unit="page">143</citedRange>
                  </bibl>.
               </note>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="PrayerDead">
               <label>Prayer for the dead</label>
               <note>See <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:SalotaEtan1951"/>, <citedRange unit="page">143-144</citedRange>
                  </bibl>.
               </note>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Dead">
               <label>Prayer for the dead (ʾƎgziʾo gǝbar tazkāra śannāya la-ʾāgbǝrtika…)</label>
               <note>Similar but not identical to <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:SalotaEtan1951"/>, <citedRange unit="page">143-144</citedRange>
               </bibl>. Probably identical to <ref type="work" corresp="LIT6452Prayer"/>.
               </note>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Thanksaakkweto">
               <label>Prayer of thanksgiving (ʾĀʾakkʷǝto la-ʾəgziʾa ṣədq wa-ʾāleʿǝl səmo la-neguśa ʿālam…) </label>
               <ab>
                  ኣአኵቶ፡ ለእግዚአ፡ ጽድቅ፡ ወኣሌዕል፡ ስሞ፡ ለንጉሠ፡ ዓለም፡ ወእሴብሕ፡ ዕበዮ፡ ለአምላከ፡ ሰማይ።
                  ነፍስየ፡ ትባርኮ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ለንጉሥ፡ ዐቢይ፡ ወትትፌሣሕ፡ ቦቱ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም። አሜን። 
                  እሴብሖ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ዘረድአኒ፡ ወእዜምር፡ ለስሙ፡ <sic corresp="JK">ለ</sic>ዑል፡ ዘፈነወ፡ 
                  ወልዶ፡ መድኅነ፡ ማሕየዌ።
               </ab>
               <note>See <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:Rome1952Saatat"/>, <citedRange unit="page">404</citedRange>
                  </bibl>, and <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:SalotaEtan1951"/>, <citedRange unit="page">146</citedRange>
                  </bibl>.
               </note>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Aakkweto">
               <label>Prayer while censing (ʾĀʾakkʷǝto la-ʾāb ʾāʾakkʷǝto la-wald ʾāʾakkʷǝto la-manfās qəddus…) </label>
               <ab>
                  ኣአኵቶ፡ ለአብ፡ ኣአኵቶ፡ ለወልድ፡ ኣአኵቶ፡ ለመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ።
               </ab>
               <note>See <bibl>
                  <ptr target="bm:Rome1952Saatat"/>, <citedRange unit="page">405</citedRange>
               </bibl>.
               </note>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Thanksemmesraw">
               <label>Prayer of thanksgiving (ʾƎm-mǝśrāq ʾəska mǝʿrāb yǝtʾakkʷat wa-yəssebbāḥ səmu la-ʾƎgziʾabəḥer…) </label>
               <ab>
                  እምሥራቅ፡ እስከ፡ ምዕራብ፡ ይትአኰት፡ ወይሴባሕ፡ ስሙ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር። እምሰሜን፡ እስከ፡ ድቡብ፡ 
                  ይትአኰት፡ ወይሴባሕ፡ ስሙ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር። እምአዜብ፡ እስከ፡ መስዕ፡ ይትአኰት፡ ወይሴባሕ፡ ስሙ፡ 
                  ለእግዚአብሔር።
               </ab>
               <note>See <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:Rome1952Saatat"/>, <citedRange unit="page">405-410</citedRange>
                  </bibl>, and <bibl>
                     <ptr target="bm:SalotaEtan1951"/>, <citedRange unit="page">147-152</citedRange>
                  </bibl>.
               </note>
            </div>
         </div>



